column2: SELECT top #  S.ObjID, S.z,L.ew, L2.ew ,L3.ew,SN.sn_# FROM SpecPhoto AS S  JOIN SpecLine AS L ON S.SpecObjID = L.SpecObjID JOIN SpecLine AS L2 ON S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID JOIN SpecLine AS L3 ON S.SpecObjID = L3.SpecObjID JOIN SpecObjAll AS SN ON S.SpecObjID = SN.SpecObjID WHERE L.LineId = # and L2.LineId = # and L3.LineID = # and (specclass=# or specclass=#) and S.zconf > .# and S.z < .# SN.sn_# > # and L2.ew > # and L3.ew > #
